node.text: @robscallon thank you so much for the awesome week! That was so much fun! I taught him how to skate a little and he showed me how to play guitar! Be on the lookout soon here for the videos on his YouTube! Ps. Also Rob, thanks for showing me the theremin and staying up late and running through some sick video games 😁💚
